{"tid":2258993,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"西環集中營：京冷待林鄭 建制跟風唔畀面","createTime":"2020-10-26T12:49:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-27T03:08:56.000Z","uid":25558,"like":27,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"7092cf0672f6f8f17ab81c9c2b66b7bddebe5fdf","tid":2258993,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T12:49:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201026/ZOYMFDQGNNB2VLX2ORRYBFE2W4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201026%2FZOYMFDQGNNB2VLX2ORRYBFE2W4%2F&d=BeC7y%2FNJ2VFG1TiFYPS6oDcZFjLth35g1vO%2BxS%2F2N%2Fg%3D&h=5c42cc7b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201026%2FZOYMFDQGNNB2VLX2ORRYBFE2W4%2F&h=83e55d9e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201026/ZOYMFDQGNNB2VLX2ORRYBFE2W4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n西環集中營：京冷待林鄭 建制跟風唔畀面<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/N9DQEAweBXvTnTG9NKu2sAROlfs=/1010x758/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/UGNM3V4BHBH63OIOLT2KJBVCBM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FN9DQEAweBXvTnTG9NKu2sAROlfs%3D%2F1010x758%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FUGNM3V4BHBH63OIOLT2KJBVCBM.jpg&h=feccbf86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n林鄭月娥<br />\n<br />\n立法會早前復會，不過正如季陶休假前所說，復會的並非新一屆議會，而是史無前例押後選舉下的延任議會，甚至連特首林鄭月娥原訂復會宣讀的施政報告，也因要先和北京開會商討而押後，何時再宣讀仍未有日期。有政界中人對季陶說，北京今次叫停了林鄭的施政報告，甚至連林鄭早已表明想月底上京商討，也不獲安排，某程度揭了林鄭的底牌，「即使外界話林鄭九成九可以連任特首，但好明顯北京根本對佢唔多重視」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中央未肯定工作<br />\n<br />\n該政界中人稱，林鄭宣佈押後公佈施政報告當日，同時說希望10月底上京與部委商討合作安排，那一晚他在一個飯局中遇上一名老資格親中人士，對方即指林鄭不是高估自己、就是不熟悉國情，「呢位親中人士話，10月尾中共召開五中全會，呢件係國家主席習近平以至全黨嘅頭等大事，妳（林鄭）以為係邊個，北京邊有人得閒招呼妳？」該親中人士更估計，隨時五中全會結束後，「等美國總統大選完埋，先得閒處理林鄭要求」。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭之後去深圳特區成立40年活動，...................................。<br />\n<br />\n有民主派中人也說，從早前曾鈺成暗批林鄭看不起建制派，到建制派因放寬兩元交通津貼向林鄭開火、連謝偉俊也說林鄭已淪為香港市長，可見連建制派也不太放林鄭在眼內，「有建制中人私下講開林鄭，都係完全唔畀面佢，因為建制自己把握到風向，以後話事係西環（中聯辦），要睇都睇西環指示，即使畀你林鄭做多屆特首，咪又話唔到事」。<br />\n<br />\n周一、五刊出"},{"pid":"e7d304986c85436b965712982124db10a1e56c93","tid":2258993,"uid":294182,"like":29,"dislike":2,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T12:50:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/91zxiyb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F91zxiyb.jpg&h=e3711c57&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"91dd0ac155974fb1db55f7eee55e298586645fcb","tid":2258993,"uid":24730,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T13:31:28.000Z","msg":"第日卸任後唔應該出公帑畀佢請保鏢，等佢流亡哈薩克搵波叔陪佢過埋下半世"},{"pid":"39052f48a23db09e29a54451629d4cc77d1b4b17","tid":2258993,"uid":108022,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T22:47:38.000Z","msg":"雜小學自身難保, 各大山頭勁多大老虎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n投靠雜小學, 咩曾割胃掛雜小學頭像, 就光速入美帝list無運行<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係人都唔敢同你班美帝list 12人frd la<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n況且佢又真係廢, 串77樣, 無功課交, 一大堆屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係正常官都shame與為伍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6260bd1bd1d80239835c7d94d57c41bd388ad4fd","tid":2258993,"uid":103916,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T23:04:24.000Z","msg":"建制派又唔係condom。"},{"pid":"148cb08ae39a6713b9ce535e0399ca45c5211a20","tid":2258993,"uid":18024,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T23:39:59.000Z","msg":"狡兔死，走狗烹<br />\n飛鳥盡，良弓藏"},{"pid":"abdf55738c3633715ad352060e399faaeaaec126","tid":2258993,"uid":14494,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T23:41:06.000Z","msg":"777唔係有習大大wechat咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4024d3d21326ffa51fe323c732e9854647aa2143","tid":2258993,"uid":51820,"lik